<paragraph id="2418850BFFA28352FC975916FB38FE35" blockId="31.[823,1477,373,590]" pageId="31" pageNumber="31">
<emphasis id="16D35919FFA28352FC975916FBF0FE76" box="[851,1120,373,397]" italics="true" pageId="31" pageNumber="31">
Notes. – 
<taxonomicName id="E3A7FE88FFA28352FC6B5915FBF0FE76" box="[943,1120,373,397]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Brassicaceae" genus="Alyssopsis" kingdom="Plantae" order="Brassicales" pageId="31" pageNumber="31" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="deflexa">Alyssopsis deflexa</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
is illegitimate because 
<bibRefCitation id="4036F8FAFFA28352FA9B5915FC19FE56" author="BOISSIER, E." pageId="31" pageNumber="31" pagination="45 - 90" refId="ref136077" refString="BOISSIER, E. (1842 a). Plantae Aucherianae orientales enumeratae, cum novarum specierum descriptione. Ann. Sci. Nat., Bot. ser. 2, 17: 45 - 90." type="journal article" year="1842">BOISSIER (1842a)</bibRefCitation>
listed the earlier published 
<taxonomicName id="E3A7FE88FFA28352FB0F59F6FB9AFE36" authority="(Aiton) W. T. Aiton" authorityName="W. T. Aiton" baseAuthorityName="Aiton" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Brassicaceae" genus="Nasturtium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Brassicales" pageId="31" pageNumber="31" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="sagittatum">
<emphasis id="16D35919FFA28352FB0F59F6FA52FE56" box="[1227,1474,406,429]" italics="true" pageId="31" pageNumber="31">Nasturtium sagittatum</emphasis>
(Aiton) W.T. Aiton
</taxonomicName>
as a synonym.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="2418850BFFA28352FC9759B5FA55FDB6" blockId="31.[823,1477,373,590]" pageId="31" pageNumber="31">
Boissier then reduced in 
<emphasis id="16D35919FFA28352FB9B59B5FAFFFE16" box="[1119,1391,469,493]" italics="true" pageId="31" pageNumber="31">
Flora Orientalis 
<taxonomicName id="E3A7FE88FFA28352FACF59B6FAFFFE16" box="[1291,1391,469,493]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Brassicaceae" genus="Alyssopsis" kingdom="Plantae" order="Brassicales" pageId="31" pageNumber="31" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="deflexa">A. deflexa</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
to synonymy of 
<taxonomicName id="E3A7FE88FFA28352FC635996FB52FDF6" authority="(Aiton) Boiss." authorityName="Boiss." baseAuthorityName="Aiton" box="[935,1218,501,525]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Brassicaceae" genus="Arabis" kingdom="Plantae" order="Brassicales" pageId="31" pageNumber="31" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="sagittata">
<emphasis id="16D35919FFA28352FC635996FB8EFDF6" box="[935,1054,502,525]" italics="true" pageId="31" pageNumber="31">A. sagittata</emphasis>
(Aiton) Boiss.
</taxonomicName>
, but his combination is illegitimate also because he listed 
<taxonomicName id="E3A7FE88FFA28352FB5C5A75FA52FDD6" authority="Jacq. (1787)" authorityName="Jacq." authorityYear="1787" box="[1176,1474,533,557]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Brassicaceae" genus="Sisymbrium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Brassicales" pageId="31" pageNumber="31" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="molle">
<emphasis id="16D35919FFA28352FB5C5A75FAD8FDD6" box="[1176,1352,533,557]" italics="true" pageId="31" pageNumber="31">Sisymbrium molle</emphasis>
Jacq. (1787)
</taxonomicName>
as a synonym, a name that predates 
<taxonomicName id="E3A7FE88FFA28352FB6A5A56FA50FDB6" authority="Aiton (1789)" authorityName="Aiton" authorityYear="1789" box="[1198,1472,565,589]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Brassicaceae" genus="Nasturtium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Brassicales" pageId="31" pageNumber="31" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="sagittatum">
<emphasis id="16D35919FFA28352FB6A5A56FAA2FDB6" box="[1198,1330,566,589]" italics="true" pageId="31" pageNumber="31">S. sagittatum</emphasis>
Aiton (1789)
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
